                    <span>I went to a spiritual retreat and found this book.  I was so deeply touched, I bought and sent copies to my friend in New York.  She said, "This book is next to the Bible." She cried and
<br />told me that since her divorce (two yrs. ago) that when she went to bed that night after reading two chapters, she didn't feel lonely; that she felt love and peace in her heart. 
<br />I read the Circle of Fire prayer and try to live it everyday.
<br />You can't go wrong with this book!  </span>
                  
