                    <span>This is another incredible book by Don Miguel Ruiz.  It is a very small book, but it's contents are enormous.  It is a book of prayers. Prayers for  forgivness, self-acceptance, etc.  It is a truely fantastic book.  Simple and powerful.  I am so greatful for having found Don Miguel Ruiz's books and I thank him for sharing his gifts with a world that so desparately needs them.</span>
                  
